01:51:38.920 --> 01:51:45.000
[Amit Varma]: So in the context of desire, how much does the nature of these languages, you know, in

01:51:45.000 --> 01:51:49.280
[Amit Varma]: being gendered and not being gendered and all of that, affect the people?

01:51:49.280 --> 01:51:51.440
