01:53:32.880 --> 01:53:38.360
[Guest]: so repression is then seen as a way of life, rather than as something that's imposed on

01:53:38.360 --> 01:53:39.360
[Guest]: you.

01:53:39.360 --> 01:53:43.680
[Guest]: Whereas we can still see repression as something that's imposed on us, because our cultural

01:53:43.680 --> 01:53:46.640
[Guest]: coordinates are all excessive, right?

01:53:46.640 --> 01:53:51.320
[Guest]: This is why the British when they came here said, Oh, my God, where have we come, right?

01:53:51.320 --> 01:53:58.240
