01:54:00.120 --> 01:54:05.840
[Guest]: The beauty of the subcontinent is that we have been a subcontinent of excess.

01:54:05.840 --> 01:54:11.400
[Guest]: And that excess also comes up just Amit, as you know, in the sheer number of languages.

01:54:11.400 --> 01:54:16.120
[Guest]: So even though many of these languages are gendered, the sheer volume and number of languages,

01:54:16.120 --> 01:54:22.880
[Guest]: dialects, versions, I said to you two weeks ago, I was in Trivandrum for the Lit Fest.

01:54:22.880 --> 01:54:25.600
