01:54:41.800 --> 01:54:43.880
[Amit Varma]: That's incredibly fascinating.

01:54:43.880 --> 01:54:48.360
[Amit Varma]: I mean, now sort of get to a question which struck me as I was reading the book that,

01:54:48.360 --> 01:54:52.120
[Amit Varma]: you know, you've got a bit in your book, for example, about how Plato's Symposium, which

01:54:52.120 --> 01:54:58.160
