01:54:58.160 --> 01:55:03.720
[Amit Varma]: And there is this tradition, which also then comes down to even the Sufis and even, you

01:55:03.720 --> 01:55:07.760
[Amit Varma]: know, you talk about maybe Ramakrishna Paramhansa and Vivekananda being an example of that,

01:55:07.760 --> 01:55:12.200
[Amit Varma]: where there is that element of desire playing out between teacher and student.

01:55:12.200 --> 01:55:14.600
[Amit Varma]: In many cases, a student might be underage.

01:55:14.600 --> 01:55:19.640
