02:04:04.200 --> 02:04:10.280
[Amit Varma]: Google and other social media, but a vast amount of data, literally big data, and then

02:04:10.280 --> 02:04:14.880
[Amit Varma]: tries to figure out because when you're searching for something on your laptop, it's a private

02:04:14.880 --> 02:04:15.880
[Amit Varma]: act.

02:04:15.880 --> 02:04:17.360
[Amit Varma]: You don't need to post it to others.

02:04:17.360 --> 02:04:18.720
[Amit Varma]: It's what you really want.

