[Amit Varma]: It reveals something about you.

02:04:20.640 --> 02:04:25.800
[Amit Varma]: And I found the book incredibly fascinating in the kind of insights it threw up for many

02:04:25.800 --> 02:04:30.000
[Amit Varma]: of which I had absolutely remotely, no explanation.

02:04:30.000 --> 02:04:34.320
